   Chen, Gao, Chinese Acad Sci, Kunming Inst Bot, Kunming Bot Garden, Kunming 650201, Yunnan, Peoples R China.
   Gao, Yong-Qian, Yunnan Forestry Technol Coll, Dept Ecol \& Environm Engn, Kunming 650224, Yunnan, Peoples R China.},
